$ %VSINSTALLDIR%\MSBuild\x.y\bin

The `x.y` can (or is?) also `current`.

(Among others), this directory contains
  • `MSBuild.exe` (Build Engine)
  • `MSBuildTaskHost.exe`
  • `Tracker.exe` (Build (MSBuild) File Tracker)
  • A → Windows/dirs/Program-Files-x86/Microsoft-Visual-Studio/version/edition/MSBuild/x_y/bin/Roslyn[`Roslyn`] subdirectory
